
## 11. **Git Ignore**

**.gitignore:**

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so
.Python
env/
venv/
.env
.venv
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# Database
*.db
*.db-journal
data/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Docker
.dockerignore
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Production
config.yaml
secrets.yaml